section: language
synopsis: Deprecate various language extensions
issues: #27329
mrs: !16145

description: {
    The following language extensions have been marked as deprecated,
    meaning they will now issue a warning with :ghc-flag:`-Wdeprecated-flags`:

    - :extension:`AlternativeLayoutRule`
    - :extension:`AlternativeLayoutRuleTransitional`
    - :extension:`ParallelArrays`
    - :extension:`PolymorphicComponents`
    - :extension:`Rank2Types`
}
